==Multiple wins and nominations==
&quot;Up to and including the 67th Annual Grammy Awards (2025)&quot;

===Wins===
* John Williams – 11 (6 consecutive)
* Howard Shore – 3 (consecutive)
* Hans Zimmer – 3
* Ludwig Göransson – 2
* Alexandre Desplat – 2
* Michael Giacchino – 2
* Hildur Guðnadóttir – 2 (consecutive)
* Alan Menken – 2 (consecutive)
* Randy Newman – 2
* Thomas Newman – 2
* Trent Reznor – 2
* Atticus Ross – 2

===Nominations===
* John Williams – 36
* Hans Zimmer – 18
* Danny Elfman – 9
* Thomas Newman – 9
* Atticus Ross – 5
* Ludwig Göransson – 4
* Trent Reznor – 4
* Alan Silvestri – 3

